parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front coil spring can cause loss of tire pressure, loss of steering control, and potentially lead to accidents, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Loud banging or rattling noise
sudden loss of tire pressure
tire damage
loss of steering control
and a plunging feeling when driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to become entangled, locked, or stuck, making it difficult or impossible for passengers to buckle up, which can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt becomes entangled
the seat belt locks or gets stuck
the seat belt does not retract properly
the seat belt becomes loose or has excessive slack
the passenger is unable to buckle up
the passenger is tightened by the belt and unable to move freely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts to repair the Takata airbag recall can lead to a delay in fixing a potentially life-threatening safety issue, putting the driver and passengers at risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Notification of recall received
but parts are unavailable for repair
dealer confirms parts are not available
manufacturer exceeds reasonable time for recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sun roof glass can cause distraction, injury, or accidents, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The sun roof glass fractures or shatters without warning
potentially causing debris to fall into the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Excessive Sun Glare from Light Interior
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive sun glare from the light interior can cause distraction, reduced visibility, and increased risk of accidents, especially on sunny days.
symptoms: Strong reflection of the dashboard on the driver's window
causing glare and distraction
especially on sunny days. Wearing sunglasses may help alleviate the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sudden Engine Stalling and Electrical System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the engine and failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls without warning
the windshield wipers stop working
the dashboard information disappears
the power brakes fail
and only the horn and emergency flasher lights remain functional.
